{"TopicId":221660,"ForumId":120,"TopicTitle":"Burn Bar Should Not Be Rounded","CreatedByName":"xTwisteDx","CreatedById":95982,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-21T19:14:14Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"xTwisteDx","CreatedById":95982,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-21T19:14:14Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe burn indicator bar, when executing a maneuver node, should not be rounded. It makes it difficult to track wether you should stop or stage at specific points along the bar. I think most users would agree that the rounded edges reduces precision a fair amount.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222023-12-22T13:29:27Z\u0022 title=\u002212/22/2023 01:29  PM\u0022 data-short=\u0022Dec 22\u0022\u003EDecember 22, 2023\u003C/time\u003E by The Space Peacock\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"The Space Peacock","CreatedById":224498,"CreatedDateTime":"2023-12-22T13:30:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/95982-xtwistedx/?do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002295982\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/profile/95982-xtwistedx/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@xTwisteDx\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0this is a suggestion, moved it out of bug reports \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}